name: LE TECOLOT (SEEKER OF THE ब्रह्माण्ड)
description:
This Owl is a seeker.  A violinist. A beautiful creature of the night.  But mostly a seeker.  The cosmic egg appears in the Vedas as Brahmanda (रह्माण्ड). 

Part of the videoart series "The Guardian" in the Tezos and Ethereum blockchains. 

960 x 540 crispy animated GIF
